\f0\fs26 \cf0 Quiver - Open harness for open models\uc0\u8232 \u8232 \
Quiver\
A self-evolving coding and research harness for the terminal, and with a Desktop app. Designed to be optimised for the best open source model, with extensible tools, transparent/ editable/ portable persistent and session memories.\
\
Apache License\
